{
  "stem": "8359.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most-- the one in the first camp, I am so scared of doctors to this day that I cannot begin to tell you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That examination, supposedly, that physical-- that was so vivid in my mind that I see myself standing there now and them looking at me and telling me to turn around.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on that basis, they decided whether I should live or die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have such fear of doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To this day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a lot of fears.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a tremendous fear of authority.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At times, we didn't think we were going to make it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know whether the will, the will to live-- but I think deep down, we all knew already by 1944 that we had nothing to go home to.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not saying that everybody-- some people did have family left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what is very much outstanding in my mind-- 1945, when the-- at the beginning of 1945 when the Russians were advancing, the Germans were sending the Jews from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were sending them-- the marches into Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one transport-- all men-- it was the first time I saw a Jewish man since 1941.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They came into our camp-- not for their benefit, because the SS marched them-- with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they needed a rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I have never seen-- [SOB]-- we looked next to them like-- like we just got back from a resort or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we tried to help them, you know, give them whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we didn't have a lot, believe me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have enough for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when we saw them, they were emaciated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
